folks were thrilled. You just have to do your sales in Paris. If anything, =
being on the New York Fashion Week schedule affords a brand more attention,=
 earlier in the seasonal cycle. <br/><br/></p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-b=
ottom:0px;"><strong>I=E2=80=99m always curious about those B-tier fashion m=
